For what it's worth, my bus makes an incredible shuttering, the whole
vehicle shakes sometimes when I'm starting out in first or second.

The list gave me some ideas, but this motor mount one makes a lot of sense.
I don't have the problem at speeds, just under the high torque of getting
started.

I'll be checking the motor mounts this weekend. It's a lot cheaper than a
rebuild anyway.

Billy


